description: The VictoryShares US Small Cap High Div Volatility Wtd ETF offers exposure to small-cap, dividend-yielding US stocks, without subjecting investors to the inherent limitations of traditional market-cap or yield weighting it. It seeks to provide investment results that track the performance of the Nasdaq Victory US Small Cap High Dividend 100 Volatility Weighted Index before fees and expenses.
name: VictoryShares US Small Cap High Div Volatility Wtd ETF
